# spheresmooth (Python)

Python implementation of basic spherical geometry utilities and scaffolding
for piecewise geodesic smoothing on the unit sphere.

This package is inspired by the R package **spheresmooth**
("Piecewise Geodesic Smoothing for Spherical Data").

## Installation

```bash
pip install -e .
